Infrastructure Development Finance
Co. may raise funds through external commercial borrowings,
Rajiv Lall, chief executive officer, said in Mumbai today.
Raising money overseas will provide more “stability” to the
company’s borrowing plans, he said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
